<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=320, user-scalable=0, initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1">
    <meta content="yes" name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable"/>
    <meta content="yes" name="apple-touch-fullscreen"/>
    <meta content="telephone=no" name="format-detection"/>
    <meta content="black" name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style">
    <title>推荐好友</title>
    <link href="../../css/user.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
</head>
<body>
<div class="sharePage">
    <p class="title">
        <em></em>
        <span>邀请好友获得奖励！</span>
    </p>
    <div class="shareInfo">
        <span>已邀请：<em>3</em>人</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        <span>获得：<em>￥15,000</em></span>
    </div>
    <div class="codeBox" style="display: none"> <!--登录之后显示自己的二维码-->
        <img src="../../images/code.png">
        <p>您的专属邀请二维码</p>
    </div>
    <div class="codeBox"> <!--没有登录默认显示的二维码-->
        <img src="../../images/code_vague.png">
        <p>登录查看您的专属二维码</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info">
        <p>• 邀请好友扫码关注公众号</p>
        <p>• 长按保存图片，发给好友或群友关注</p>
        <p>• 点击右上角，告诉更多朋友<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;具体文案待确认</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>